The salon has been operating for years and has attracted a lot of customers who are mostly students and those who have finished school and stay a bit far and travel longer distances to get to the salon. The salon caters for different needs ranging from if you want a barber, there are several barbers that you can select from, nail techs who offer ranges of different styles of nails. Also, hair stylists whom each deal with different hair types and show recommendations to the types of hair products that you use to maintain your hair.</p>
